title: Lamar Odom Reportedly Found Unconscious in Las Vegas Brothel
text:
According to TMZ , Lamar Odom was found unconscious on Tuesday at the Love Ranch South in Pahrump, Nev. It is believed that Odom arrived on Saturday and allegedly seen "taking an herbal substitute for Viagra." When the former NBA star was found, he was rolled over and fluid started coming out of his mouth. At a nearby hospital, Odom underwent intubation, suggesting that he needed help to breathe.
TMZ is reporting that he was "airlifted from the hospital to Las Vegas for more treatment." We will update you with more information when it becomes available.
[via TMZ ]
